description:
Transformers: Fall of Cybertron - Multiplayer Havoc Pack is an action-shooter game developed by High Moon Studios. It came out on 24-08-2012. It was published by High Moon Studios. The game is rated as "Skip" on RAWG.
You can play Transformers: Fall of Cybertron - Multiplayer Havoc Pack on PlayStation 3 and PC.
